You will NOT rob me, you will NOT rob my family, and you will NOT rob those involved in making this product that have to be paid. This money does not belong to you. One HOUR. Failure to comply will result in me exposing your page. I have the screens shots to prove it. Trust me. I've already hit you up privately but you're still selling my stuff. One HOUR.
Issue resolved. Black entrepreneurship matters.

Excited releasing the second single “IT GETS BETTER” from my upcoming Gospel project on all streaming platforms.

“It Gets Better” was written in response to the suicides of teenagers who are bullied because of their sexual orientation or because their peers suspected that they were gay. I hope this song inspires the LGBTQ community and their allies from around the world, sending the the message that life will improve as you grow older, and once you are able to abandon toxic relationship and situations. 

For more information on how you can help this cause please visit the organization’s website at: https://itgetsbetter.org The It Gets Better Project’s mission is to uplift, empower, and connect lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, and queer (LGBTQ+) youth around the globe.

Thank you for all the wonderful collaborators below that help me make it BETTER.
